data.title: Usher's ex-wife Tameka Foster thought he was already married to Jennifer Goicoechea
data.meta_description: Usher's ex-wife Tameka Foster has revealed she was surprised by his Las Vegas wedding on Super Bowl Sunday (11.02.24) because she thought he was already married to Jennifer Goicoechea.
data.text:
Usher's ex-wife Tameka Foster has revealed she was surprised by his Las Vegas wedding on Super Bowl Sunday (11.02.24) because she thought he was already married to Jennifer Goicoechea.
